==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nostoc
<hw>Nos"toc</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of algae. The plants are composed of
moniliform cells imbedded in a gelatinous substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ <spn>Nostoc commune</spn> is found on the ground, and is
ordinarily not seen; but after a rain it swells up into a conspicuous
jellylike mass, which was formerly supposed to have fallen from the sky,
whence the popular names, <stype>fallen star</stype> and <stype>star
jelly</stype>. Also called <stype>witches' butter</stype>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nostocaceae</ent>⟦br⟧
